::Killfest/Scyther::

Killfest looks over the shuttle, frowning. Scyther comes up near him, 
also looking at it.

"How many of them do you want me to get?" Scyther asks thoughtfully, 
his mind going through various calculations.

"As many as you can get. We need some help here," comes the reply 
from Killfest.

Scyther turns to Chamaleon. "How many bots can that shuttle hold?"


(Reminder: bot capacity limit for a craft is three bots)
